    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Personal articles of a bride, usually including clothing, accessories, and household linens; the term derives from an original meaning of "bundle," referring to the manner in which the items were bound and carried to the bride's new home.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
